    "Popskill 帮你把一份 AI 技能装一次，同时挂给 Claude Code 和 Codex 等工具。\n粘贴一个 GitHub 仓库或本地文件夹，就能开始。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Popskill installs an AI skill once and links it to tools like Claude Code and Codex at the same time.\nPaste a GitHub repo or a local folder to get started."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Popskill 帮你把一份 AI 技能装一次，同时挂给 Claude Code 和 Codex 等工具。\n粘贴一个 GitHub 仓库或本地文件夹，就能开始。"
