    "launchctl unload——不再按时执行，plist 文件原样保留，随时可重新启用。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "launchctl unload — stops scheduled runs; the plist file stays untouched and can be re-enabled anytime."
