            "value": "Equivalent to launchctl kickstart -k — runs it once right now without waiting for the next scheduled time. Check the task's own log for output."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "等价于 launchctl kickstart -k——不等下次调度时间，现在就跑一遍。任务输出看它自己的日志。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
